{"tid":1346333,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗恐襲係中共常用手段 \b[黑幫外判鎮壓] [Thugs-for-hire]","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T14:52:29.000Z","uid":275507,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4abe8078ab9a3d72feecccbf671d124715d3a5ea","tid":1346333,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要應清事實，將矛頭指向政府，警隊。文宣幫手做野，將元朗恐襲指責同政府拉翻埋一齊！<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<strong>Why does the Chinese gov&rsquo;t need to hire thugs to exert social control?</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2018/11/04/chinese-govt-need-hire-thugs-exert-social-control/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2018%2F11%2F04%2Fchinese-govt-need-hire-thugs-exert-social-control%2F&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=ef73a1d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2018/11/04/chinese-govt-need-hire-thugs-exert-social-control/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Thugs and Outsourcing of State Repression in China</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/322488668_Thugs_and_Outsourcing_of_State_Repression_in_China\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F322488668_Thugs_and_Outsourcing_of_State_Repression_in_China&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=432b4821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.researchgate.net/publication/322488668_Thugs_and_Outsourcing_of_State_Repression_in_China</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/perspectives-on-politics/article/thugsforhire-subcontracting-of-state-coercion-and-state-capacity-in-china/C53871B8B259B893E1D0B4E1985B764E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fjournals%2Fperspectives-on-politics%2Farticle%2Fthugsforhire-subcontracting-of-state-coercion-and-state-capacity-in-china%2FC53871B8B259B893E1D0B4E1985B764E&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=3ba658ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/perspectives-on-politics/article/thugsforhire-subcontracting-of-state-coercion-and-state-capacity-in-china/C53871B8B259B893E1D0B4E1985B764E</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&quot;中國會使用黑幫外判鎮壓當鎮壓行為是非法或政策不受歡迎、逃避責任或當國家的能力不如社會強大時。 &quot;<br />\n&quot;中國常以黑幫外判鎮壓手段以驅逐房主，實施一孩政策，橫徵暴斂，鎮壓請願者和抗議者。&quot;</span><br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"854c317ab848237ad5965334350c0a63a77193c1","tid":1346333,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f00347699d25a056202fd59e00c434295ddcff4","tid":1346333,"uid":20024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:04:27.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉，希望大家討論吓不同意見既成效<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1. 短期內舉辦光復元朗行動<br />\n<br />\n2. 搜集任何相關資料，包括但不限有關人仕個人資料，相關物業/店舖資料，活躍地點，行蹤等等<br />\n<br />\n<del>3. 透過海關，入境，警方，食環等等相關部門，清洗元朗黃賭毒產業鏈 ，烏煙瘴氣</del><span style=\"color: red;\">好多巴打覺得警黑合作，成效不大</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 眾籌去聘請例如G4S/黑水等國際保安公司，保護各議員，知名人仕如陳伯，記者們，其他有需要市民等等<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">好多巴打贊成呢個方案</span><br />\n<br />\n5. 元朗放盤/退租，警黑合作，治安全無<br />\n<br />\n6. 舉報僭建<br />\n<br />\n7. 全民對抗新鴻基SHK運動</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[集思廣益]發夢夢到殲滅元朗官商鄉黑計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1342215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1342215</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[發夢][眾籌]聘請G4S/黑水保護議員，記者，陳伯，市民等是否可行？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1343417\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1343417</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[發夢][不合作][長期]元朗放盤/退租行動，考慮吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345525</a><br />\n- 分享自 